<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Kinger Matrimonials</title>
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cormorant+Garamond:wght@500;600;700&family=Manrope:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/style.css" />
</head>
<body class="theme-shell">
  <header class="hero">
    <nav class="site-nav">
      <a class="brand" href="/">Kinger Matrimonials</a>
      <div class="nav-links">
        <a href="/gun-milan">Gun Milan</a>
        <a href="/admin/login">Admin Login</a>
        <a href="/member/login">Member Login</a>
        <a href="/submit" class="nav-button">Submit Biodata</a>
      </div>
    </nav>

    <div class="hero-grid">
      <section class="hero-copy">
        <p class="eyebrow">Trusted Matrimonial Support</p>
        <h1>Warm introductions, verified details, and a more graceful way to find the right match.</h1>
        <p class="hero-text">
          Kinger Matrimonials helps families and individuals submit biodata, review serious profiles,
          and stay connected through a simple, respectful process.
        </p>
        <div class="hero-actions">
          <a href="/submit" class="primary-button">Start Your Profile</a>
          <a href="/gun-milan" class="secondary-button">Check Gun Milan</a>
          <a href="/admin/login" class="secondary-button">Admin Login</a>
        </div>
      </section>

      <aside class="hero-panel">
        <div class="stat-card">
          <span class="stat-label">Approved Profiles</span>
          <strong><%= approvedCount %></strong>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-card">
          <span class="stat-label">Pending Reviews</span>
          <strong><%= pendingCount %></strong>
        </div>
        <div class="highlight-card">
          <p class="highlight-title">Private and reviewed</p>
          <ul class="feature-list">
            <li>Structured biodata submissions</li>
            <li>Admin review before approvals go live</li>
            <li>Member login enabled only after approval</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </aside>
    </div>
  </header>

  <main class="content-shell">
    <section class="section-grid">
      <article class="info-card">
        <p class="section-kicker">How it works</p>
        <h2>Three simple steps, handled with care</h2>
        <div class="process-list">
          <div>
            <span>01</span>
            <h3>Submit your biodata</h3>
            <p>Share your details, photo, and biodata PDF in one guided form.</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <span>02</span>
            <h3>Get reviewed</h3>
            <p>Each submission is checked by the admin team before approval.</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <span>03</span>
            <h3>Stay updated</h3>
            <p>You receive email confirmation when your profile is approved.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>

      <article class="info-card accent-card">
        <p class="section-kicker">For families and candidates</p>
        <h2>Clear profiles, simple communication, and a softer first impression.</h2>
        <p>
          This platform is designed to reduce friction: less chasing, fewer missing documents,
          and a cleaner review process for everyone involved.
        </p>
      </article>
    </section>

    <section class="recent-section">
      <div class="section-heading">
        <div>
          <p class="section-kicker">Private discovery</p>
          <h2>Approved profiles are shared only with approved members</h2>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="empty-card">
        <h3>Private member browsing only</h3>
        <p>Approved profile names, photos, and biodata are not shown publicly. Once your own profile is approved, we send a password setup email so you can log in privately.</p>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</body>
</html>
